<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Formal-Review :: Tag :: hyunyoun's Blog</title><link>https://buenhyden.github.io/tags/formal-review.html</link><description/><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>chochyjj@gmail.com (Hyunyoun Jo)</managingEditor><webMaster>chochyjj@gmail.com (Hyunyoun Jo)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 07:09:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://buenhyden.github.io/tags/formal-review/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>감사(Audit)</title><link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/audit.html</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 07:09:00 +0000</pubDate><author>chochyjj@gmail.com (Hyunyoun Jo)</author><guid>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/audit.html</guid><description>독립적인 검토자들이 소프트웨어 산출물과 프로세스를 체계적으로 검사하고 평가하는 공식적인 검토 과정이다.</description></item><item><title>Inspection</title><link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/inspection.html</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 07:08:00 +0000</pubDate><author>chochyjj@gmail.com (Hyunyoun Jo)</author><guid>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/inspection.html</guid><description>인스펙션은 FTR(Formal Technical Review)라고도 불리며, 정형화된 절차와 체크리스트를 사용하여 소프트웨어 산출물의 결함을 찾아내는 방법이다.</description></item><item><title>관리 검토(Management Review)</title><link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/management-review.html</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 07:08:00 +0000</pubDate><author>chochyjj@gmail.com (Hyunyoun Jo)</author><guid>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/qa/qc/deliverable-verification/peer-review/formal-review/management-review.html</guid><description>관리 검토는 소프트웨어 개발 프로젝트의 진행 상황, 목표 달성도, 리스크 등을 경영진과 프